      <title>罗技与创始人就新任董事长的争议可能会推迟年度股东大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/logitech-dispute-with-founder-over-new-chairman-may-delay-agm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗技国际公司 (Logitech International SA) 创始人丹尼尔·博雷尔 (Daniel Borel) 获得法院判决，由于他继续就新董事长的任命提出异议，该公司年度股东大会可能会被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/logitech-dispute-with-founder-over-new-chairman-may-delay-agm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 17:37:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
